    "body": "## Summary\n\nAdd backward pass support for SM120 (Blackwell GeForce / DGX Spark). SM120 uses SM80-era MMA instructions (`mma.sync.aligned.m16n8k16`) with 99 KB shared memory (vs 163 KB on SM80).\n\n- `FlashAttentionBackwardSm120` subclass overrides `can_implement()` with SM120 SMEM capacity (99 KB)\n- SM120 backward tile config: m=n=64, stages=1 (D>64) or 2 (D≤64), 128 threads (4 warps, all in M-direction)\n- Pre/postprocess kernels use SM80 code paths (`post_arch=80`)\n- Skips head_dim validation (SM120 not in the validation table) and preserves 128 threads (no override to 384)\n\nDepends on PR #2329 (SM120 forward pass).\n\n## Validation\n\nTested on SM121a (DGX Spark, NVIDIA GB10) with BF16 across 14 configurations:\n\n| Head dim | Seq len | Causal | dq_max | dk_max | dv_max |\n|----------|---------|--------|--------|--------|--------|\n| 64 | 256 | No | 0.0039 | 0.0039 | 0.0039 |\n| 64 | 256 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0078 | 0.0156 |\n| 64 | 512 | No | 0.0039 | 0.0039 | 0.0039 |\n| 64 | 512 | Yes | 0.0078 | 0.0098 | 0.0156 |\n| 96 | 256 | No | 0.0039 | 0.0039 | 0.0039 |\n| 96 | 256 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0156 | 0.0156 |\n| 96 | 512 | No | 0.0039 | 0.0039 | 0.0020 |\n| 96 | 512 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0156 | 0.0313 |\n| 128 | 256 | No | 0.0039 | 0.0078 | 0.0039 |\n| 128 | 256 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0156 | 0.0313 |\n| 128 | 512 | No | 0.0020 | 0.0020 | 0.0020 |\n| 128 | 512 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0078 | 0.0313 |\n| 128 | 1024 | No | 0.0020 | 0.0020 | 0.0020 |\n| 128 | 1024 | Yes | 0.0156 | 0.0156 | 0.0156 |\n\nAll 14/14 tests pass. Gradient max diffs < 0.032 (BF16 expected range).\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] Run backward pass tests on SM121a hardware\n- [ ] Verify D=64/96/128 × causal/non-causal gradient correctness\n- [ ] Ensure no regression on SM90/SM100 backward paths\n\nContributed by Second Nature Computing (https://joinsecondnature.com)",
